text: Bik-Karmaly () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Bik-Karmalinsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 324 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km from Davlekanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Bik-Karmaly
